    "introHtml": "<p>Ranked for a cheap fun second car — <strong>condition over miles</strong>. Preference for reliable platforms (Solstice/Sky, Miata, BMW inline-6), low-mileage survivors, working top, and no rust or salvage history. Manual preferred. All picks within 35 miles of Media, PA (ZIP 19063). Refreshed <strong>May 14, 2026</strong>. Sources: Cars.com (24 listings, clean-title+no-accident filter), CarGurus (112 total), AutoTrader (99 total). TrueCar URL broken on first run — fix slug for next refresh.</p>",
