        "whyGood": "The NC-generation Miata (2006-2015) is the most reliable, refined, and parts-supported sports convertible under $15k. 82k miles is barely middle age for an NC. The Touring trim adds leather, heated seats, and a Bose stereo. No accidents reported. Dealer listing from a Lexus store suggests a proper trade-in inspection.",
