        "whyGood": "The E88 128i carries BMW's N52 naturally-aspirated 3.0L inline-6 — one of the smoothest, most reliable BMW engines ever, unlike the turbocharged N54/N55 in the 135i. At $9,500 with 69k miles and a Great Deal badge this is significantly underpriced. The 128i convertible is rare and underappreciated.",
