        "whyGood": "The E46 325Ci is widely regarded as one of the best-handling BMWs ever. 60,200 miles on a 2001 is exceptional — barely driven over 24 years. No accidents, clean title from Cars.com filter. The M54 inline-6 is smooth, tuneful, and well-proven.",
