        "whyGood": "The Z3 2.8 with the M52 straight-six is night-and-day better than the four-cylinder Z3. 75k miles, no accidents, very close to Media. The Z3 roadster top is a simple manually-latched fabric unit — nothing electronic to fail. Classic proportions and a great weekend road car.",
